snippet.title: Rugby25 | Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Here we are! Rugby 25 is officially launching its Early Access!

In this initial Early Access release you will be able to select from 21 Nations, but the only team with photogrammetry will be the Australian Wallabies and French Teams. Other teams and photogrammetry will be constantly added as the Early Access period progresses.

Our goal with this Early Access is to eventually include over 140 International Teams including New Zealand, South Africa, England, France and Australia. Over 150 Club Sides, 11 competitions and more !

Follow us on Twitter for more informations : Twitter ► https://x.com/rugbythegame
